  { q: 'Is it safe to paste Zalgo text everywhere?', a: 'Most modern apps handle it fine. Very old or minimalist interfaces may render it oddly or clip it. Use the Mini intensity for safer use.' },
  { q: 'What intensity levels are available?', a: 'Mini (subtle), Normal (medium glitch), and Maxi (extreme corruption).' },
  { q: 'Can Zalgo text break websites?', a: 'Modern browsers and apps handle Unicode combining marks correctly. Some very old systems may have layout issues with extreme Zalgo text.' },
];
